### Welcome to the SNAP GitHub Pages.
![SNAP Logo](http://www.snap.uaf.edu/images/snap_acronym_rgb.png)
This page is part of the "ua-snap" pages, intended to hightlight technical information about the products and repositories maintained by the Scenarios Network for Alaska Planning.  You can find our main page at http://www.snap.uaf.edu
